item.description: I'm trying to get a regular climbing thing going. I'm a teacher so the summer is pretty wide open for me. Recently replaced my rope, I also have some trad gear (though sadly can't locate my mid-sized cams) and several slings and about 15 quick-draws. I'll post this in a few meetup groups and throw times around with my local buddies... majority rules!
